title: MONDAY - Week 16 Playoff picture becomes clearer 2020
itunes:title: MONDAY - Week 16 Playoff picture becomes clearer 2020
description:
The playoff picture starting to take shape after Sunday. The Packers showing they are the class of the NFC with a big win over the Titans (0:11). The Steelers clinch the AFC North (1:31) with come-from-behind win over the Colts, while the Chiefs (2:34) secure the number one seed in the AFC by beating the Falcons. In the NFC, the Seahawks capture the West division (3:23) by taking down division rivals, The Rams as Jamal Adams looking for some R-E-S-P-E-C-T for his defense (3:51)
